{
  //########################################
  // Dialogues for Dwarf
  //########################################

  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Introduction": "Hey, you're pretty good at mining, for a human.",

  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Mon": "I got all this stuff from the surface. I just take it from your people during the night.#$e#Hmm? What is this concept you call \"private property\"?",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Tue": "Ah... cave carrot stew, cave carrot roast, cave carrot soup and cave carrots au gratin.#$e#...And a ramekin of cave carrot brulee to sweeten the night.#$e#What?",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Wed": "Hey, wanna buy something?",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Wed_6": "Long ago, my people knew the secrets of advanced technology. The archaeological evidence proves that.#$e#But I wonder where it came from? And where did it all go? I guess some questions will never be answered...",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Thu_4": "I feel most comfortable underground.#$e#The deeper underground the better.",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Fri": "You've never seen a dwarf before, have you?",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Sat_8": "The mines can be a treacherous place. Be careful, friend.",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Sat": "It's dangerous in the mines. Why don't you buy a few things from my shop to ensure your safety?",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Sun": "One day you'll have to tell me about this beverage you call \"milk\".",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Thu": "You're not a spy sent by the Shadow People, are you?#$e#I'm keeping my eye on you.",
  "Dwarf.Dialogue.Fri_2": "Most humans fear the unknown... that's why I've hidden my shop here.#$e#Your mining skills prove you're trustworthy."
}